transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haanji sir aaj baat nahi ho payegi abhi.
Executive: Sir main aapse thoda sa busy hu.
Customer: Kya sir?
Executive: Ji sir busy hai. Busy in rehne se toh bataiye aap.
Customer: Sir aapki aawaz thodi slow si ho rahi hai.
Executive: Jab main aapko call mein phone karta hu.
Executive: Accha sir kitni der mein call karna hai?
Customer: But mujhe lag raha hai thoda ki na hai.
Executive: Kya?
Customer: Koi matlab nahi hai tab toh baat hogi.
Customer: Theek hai na? Ab main nahi banaunga.
summary:
